citations:
    citation-asos-arya-vi:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Arya VI"
            text_from_source: "The brotherhood without banners... When we left King's Landing we were men of Winterfell and men of Darry and men of Blackhaven... Six score of us set out to bring the king's justice to your brother."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Arya and Gendry are brought hooded to the hollow hill, the Brotherhood Without Banners' hidden cave. Sandor Clegane is brought in as prisoner by the Mad Huntsman. Lord Beric Dondarrion presides. Sandor is accused of crimes of House Clegane. He demands trial by combat. Beric fights Sandor with a flaming sword. Sandor wins — his cold steel cleaves through Beric's burning blade and into his chest. Thoros then miraculously resurrects Beric. Sandor is declared innocent by the Lord of Light's judgment and freed."
